<p style="text-align:justify"><font color="#FFFFFF">
<span style="text-decoration: none; font-weight:700">At the end of the 19<sup>th</sup> century 
almost a million tourists were visiting annually Monaco and casino Monte Carlo, 
when in 1850s the number was less than 200. Monte Carlo became a favorite 
playground and gambling Mecca for players, aristocracy and members of the Royal 
families, self-made millionaires and great artists. </span><b>Learn 
more about the history of gambling, including the emergence of <u>
<a style="color: #0000FF" href="http://www.jackpot.co.uk">online casinos</a></u>, 
by visiting Jackpot.co.uk<span lang="en-us">.</span></b></font></p>
